title: El Farolito with Mookie Blaiklock (LIVE)
itunes:title: El Farolito with Mookie Blaiklock (LIVE)
description:
Mookie Blaiklock (YOU ARE WORTHY with LilMookieB) joins to 'boys to rap about their preferred burritos before a review of El Farolito. Plus, Snack or Wack with cookies from Golden Gate Fortune Cookie Factory. Recorded live at The Palace of Fine Arts Theatre in San Francisco 6/10/22.
